subject: JUnit article 'front page' of Builder.com
msgSnippet: ZDNet was touting an improved builder.com website, so I surfed over to www.builder.com (which redirected to builder.com.com ... huh!) and there was a lead
messageBody:
ZDNet was touting an improved 'builder.com' website,
so I surfed over to www.builder.com (which redirected
to builder.com.com ... huh!) and there was a lead
article about JUnit test cases.

Richard.
